content:
You now get all the benefits of second-generation managed packaging for Data Cloud features. When you package Data Cloud metadata, add it to a data kit first and then add the data kit to a package. Data Cloud apps must contain only Data Cloud metadata.

Where: This change applies to second-generation managed packages.

When: This functionality is available starting in April 2024.

Who: Data Cloud Second-Generation Managed Packaging is available only to Salesforce Partners.
title: Salesforce Summer '24 Release Notes
